<ab facs="#facs_220_r1l4">genant hanns hawg den <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> vom Stein <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd in ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_220_r1l5">dechtnuſſ hab / daʒ er <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>kuntſchaft<ex>er</ex></expan> auf Jn ſüll ſeın etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_220_r1l6">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> niht wıſſend </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_220_r1l7">vnd <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> eẅr armman <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>nthalben</expan> vnſchuldıg ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_220_r1l8">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_220" id="109r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Annen, Hannsen von Puttendorff <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>iebe</ex></expan> fraw, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von ein
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> armmanns <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        genant Hanns Hawg, den <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> vom Stein <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und in verdechtnuss hab, daz er <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>kuntschaft<ex>er</ex></expan> auf in süll sein etc., das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> niht wissend und
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> ewr armman
                            <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>nthalben</expan> unschuldig ist. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>.</ab>
</div>
